    "body": "## Problem\r\nWhen ui2 is enabled, indenting with = pops up two messages.\r\n```\r\n{x-1} lines to indent...\r\n{x} lines indented\r\n```\r\nwhereas in ui1, it's only displayed as one line\r\n```\r\n{x} lines indented\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nFinal indentation message now overwrites previous ones\r\n\r\nCloses #39212",
    "closed_at": null,
