            "body": "Done. I wasn't sure where to put the test. Is there a better place for it ?\r\nAlso, there are two ways of approaching this issue :\r\n-  The last message overwrites the previous one only when there is a single \"intermediate\" message\r\n-  Each message overwrites the previous one\r\n\r\nI'm not sure what's the best here. I went for the second option.",
