            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "The ui1 behavior is also to just overwrite any message so I think we can set it to true unconditionally (try `map = <cmd>echom \"foo\" <bar> norm! =G<CR>`).\n```suggestion\n        msg_ext_overwrite = true;\n```",
